   <collaboration id="sid-62d9b66d-de17-44f4-ac8e-b36fdbad09e6">
      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="A Subsequent Delivery Free of Charge order typically refers to additional deliveries made after an initial transaction where the customer is not charged for the product or services provided. This could be due to Various reasons such as replacement or exchange, customer receives lesser number of goods than that ordered, or goods have been damaged in the shipment. It allows to track and process orders while ensuring accurate inventory management and customer satisfaction."/>
